data.description: This spacious 2-story home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. On the main level, you'll find a welcoming foyer that leads into a generously sized living room, complemented by an elegant dining area. The open-concept kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient island, making it a chef's dream.Upstairs, the four bedrooms provide ample space for family and guests, with the owners suite featuring a private en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. The other bedrooms share a well-appointed full bathroom. A half-bath is conveniently located on the first floor for guests. The 2-car garage and a spacious backyard complete this home, making it a versatile and ideal space for families and entertaining.
